<html xmlns:o="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" xmlns:w="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<title>Travejor — Cute Mode Icon Manifest</title>
<style>
  body { font-family: Calibri, Arial, sans-serif; color: #2c2318; font-size: 11pt; }
  h1 { color: #f7941d; font-size: 22pt; margin-bottom: 2pt; }
  h2 { color: #2c2318; font-size: 14pt; border-bottom: 2px solid #f7941d;
       padding-bottom: 3pt; margin-top: 22pt; }
  .sub { color: #948b7c; font-size: 10pt; margin-top: 0; }
  table { border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin: 8pt 0; }
  th { background: #f7941d; color: #ffffff; text-align: left;
       padding: 5pt 8pt; font-size: 10pt; }
  td { border: 1px solid #e6dac3; padding: 5pt 8pt; font-size: 10pt;
       vertical-align: top; }
  .have { color: #12a07a; font-weight: bold; }
  .need { color: #ef5d3c; font-weight: bold; }
  .icon { font-family: Consolas, monospace; }
  .note { background: #fdf4e6; border-left: 4px solid #f7941d;
          padding: 8pt 12pt; font-size: 10pt; margin: 10pt 0; }
  .summary th { background: #2c2318; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<h1>Travejor — Cute Mode Icon Manifest</h1>
<p class="sub">A third app theme (Light / Dark / Cute) using hand-painted watercolor
icons. This document lists every graphic element in the app.<br/>
<b>Legend:</b> <span class="have">HAVE</span> = already in the supplied asset
sets &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; <span class="need">NEED</span> = must be produced.</p>

<h2>A &middot; Brand &amp; Identity</h2>
<table>
<tr><th>Icon name</th><th>Use</th><th>Status</th></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">app_logo</td><td>Top-bar wordmark</td><td class="have">HAVE</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">paper_plane</td><td>Brand motif / loading</td><td class="have">HAVE</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">susen_orb</td><td>S.U.S.E.N AI mark</td><td class="need">NEED</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">susen_thinking</td><td>AI typing / loading state</td><td class="need">NEED</td></tr>
</table>

<h2>B &middot; Bottom Navigation (5)</h2>
<table>
<tr><th>Icon name</th><th>Use</th><th>Status</th></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">nav_home</td><td>Home tab</td><td class="have">HAVE</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">nav_tools</td><td>Tools tab</td><td class="have">HAVE</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">nav_feed</td><td>Feed tab</td><td class="have">HAVE</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">nav_profile</td><td>Profile tab</td><td class="have">HAVE</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">nav_susen</td><td>Centre Susen orb</td><td class="need">NEED</td></tr>
</table>

<h2>C &middot; Home — Radial Hub (5) — already applied</h2>
<table>
<tr><th>Icon name</th><th>Use</th><th>Status</th></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">hub_meet</td><td>Meet up</td><td class="have">HAVE</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">hub_events</td><td>Events nearby</td><td class="have">HAVE</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">hub_todo</td><td>What to do</td><td class="have">HAVE</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">hub_eat</td><td>What to eat</td><td class="have">HAVE</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">hub_stay</td><td>Where to stay</td><td class="have">HAVE</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">hub_center_map</td><td>Centre "Where to next" orb</td><td class="need">NEED</td></tr>
</table>

<h2>D &middot; Traveler Toolbox — 12 Categories &nbsp;(biggest gap)</h2>
<table>
<tr><th>Icon name</th><th>Use</th><th>Status</th></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">atm</td><td>ATMs</td><td class="have">HAVE</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">public_wifi</td><td>Public Wi-Fi</td><td class="have">HAVE</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">currency_exchange</td><td>Currency exchange</td><td class="have">HAVE</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">transportation</td><td>Transport</td><td class="have">HAVE</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">market</td><td>Markets / shops</td><td class="need">NEED</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">bank</td><td>Banks</td><td class="need">NEED</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">sim_card</td><td>SIM cards</td><td class="need">NEED</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">bathroom</td><td>Public restrooms</td><td class="need">NEED</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">medical_clinic</td><td>Clinics / pharmacies</td><td class="need">NEED</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">police</td><td>Police stations</td><td class="need">NEED</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">embassy</td><td>Embassies</td><td class="need">NEED</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">laundry</td><td>Laundry</td><td class="need">NEED</td></tr>
</table>

<h2>E &middot; Map &amp; Location</h2>
<table>
<tr><th>Icon name</th><th>Status</th></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">map_pin, user_marker, group_marker, gps_locate, direction_arrow,
compass_ring, route_line, venue_highlight, heat_zone</td><td class="have">HAVE (9)</td></tr>
</table>

<h2>F &middot; Status &amp; Badges</h2>
<table>
<tr><th>Icon name</th><th>Status</th></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">status_online, status_offline, status_busy, status_traveling,
status_nearby, active_now, verified, premium, new_user, connected, loading,
success, error, warning</td><td class="have">HAVE (14)</td></tr>
</table>

<h2>G &middot; Social &amp; Communication</h2>
<table>
<tr><th>Icon name</th><th>Status</th></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">chat_bubble, voice_message, video_call, call, typing, mention,
emoji, gif, like, comment, share, follow, friend_request, group_join, invite,
