</table>

<h2>H &middot; UI Controls &amp; Actions &nbsp;(gap)</h2>
<table>
<tr><th>Icon name</th><th>Status</th></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">search, plus_add, bell, heart_save, star, lock, calendar,
mail</td><td class="have">HAVE (8)</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">close_x, back_arrow, chevron_up, chevron_down, chevron_left,
chevron_right, menu_kebab, settings_gear, filter, edit_pencil, trash_delete,
check, info, eye, eye_off, clock, refresh, send, bookmark, external_link</td>
<td class="need">NEED (20)</td></tr>
</table>

<h2>I &middot; Profile &amp; Account</h2>
<table>
<tr><th>Icon name</th><th>Status</th></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">profile_avatar, camera_change_photo, passport, globe, flag</td>
<td class="have">HAVE (5)</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">traveler_status_exploring, traveler_status_local,
traveler_status_transit, traveler_status_offline, instagram_badge,
edit_profile</td><td class="need">NEED (6)</td></tr>
</table>

<h2>J &middot; Rating &amp; Quality (Toolbox)</h2>
<table>
<tr><th>Icon name</th><th>Use</th><th>Status</th></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">backpack_filled</td><td>Backpack rating (filled)</td><td class="need">NEED</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">backpack_empty</td><td>Backpack rating (empty)</td><td class="need">NEED</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">balloon_red</td><td>Marker badge — rating 3&ndash;4</td><td class="need">NEED</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">balloon_green</td><td>Marker badge — rating 4&ndash;4.5</td><td class="need">NEED</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">thumbs_up_orange</td><td>Marker badge — rating 4.5+</td><td class="need">NEED</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">top_pick_badge</td><td>Card "Top pick" badge</td><td class="need">NEED</td></tr>
</table>

<h2>K &middot; Empty-State Illustrations &nbsp;(larger spot art)</h2>
<table>
<tr><th>Illustration name</th><th>Use</th><th>Status</th></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">empty_no_messages</td><td>No chats yet</td><td class="need">NEED</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">empty_no_travelers</td><td>No travelers nearby</td><td class="need">NEED</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">empty_no_events</td><td>No events</td><td class="need">NEED</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">empty_no_saved_places</td><td>No saved places</td><td class="need">NEED</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">empty_no_notifications</td><td>All caught up</td><td class="need">NEED</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">empty_no_bookings</td><td>No trips booked</td><td class="need">NEED</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">empty_no_results</td><td>Search — no matches</td><td class="need">NEED</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">illustration_error</td><td>Error screen</td><td class="need">NEED</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">illustration_offline</td><td>Offline screen</td><td class="need">NEED</td></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">illustration_loading</td><td>Loading screen</td><td class="need">NEED</td></tr>
</table>

<h2>L &middot; Travel &amp; Content (Toolbox map / Vibes / Feed)</h2>
<table>
<tr><th>Icon name</th><th>Status</th></tr>
<tr><td class="icon">plane, hostel, tent, beach, mountain, island, campfire, bar,
club, restaurant, street_food, surfing, pub_crawl, safety_zone, scooter, train,
ferry, taxi, coffee, music</td><td class="have">HAVE (20)</td></tr>
</table>

<h2>Summary — Still To Produce</h2>
<table class="summary">
<tr><th>Priority</th><th>Set</th><th>Count</th></tr>
<tr><td>HIGH</td><td>Toolbox category icons (market, bank, sim_card, bathroom,
medical_clinic, police, embassy, laundry)</td><td>8</td></tr>
<tr><td>HIGH</td><td>UI control icons (close, back, chevrons, gear, filter, edit,
trash, check, send&hellip;)</td><td>~20</td></tr>
<tr><td>MEDIUM</td><td>Empty-state illustrations</td><td>10</td></tr>
<tr><td>MEDIUM</td><td>Rating system (backpacks, balloons, thumb, top-pick)</td><td>~7</td></tr>
<tr><td>LOW</td><td>Traveler status (4), Susen orb states (3), nav_susen,
hub_center, instagram, edit_profile</td><td>~11</td></tr>
<tr><td><b>TOTAL NEEDED</b></td><td><b>New graphics to produce</b></td><td><b>~56</b></td></tr>
<tr><td><b>ALREADY HAVE</b></td><td><b>Map, Status, Social, Travel, partial UI</b></td><td><b>~115</b></td></tr>
</table>

<div class="note">
<b>Production note:</b> The UI Control icons (Section H) are tiny 16&ndash;20&nbsp;px
icons that must recolor for active/inactive states. Detailed watercolor raster
reads poorly at that size &mdash; produce these as <b>simple flat watercolor
shapes</b>, or keep them as SVG line icons even in Cute mode.
</div>

<div class="note">
<b>Specs for all icons:</b> transparent PNG, square canvas, 512&times;512&nbsp;px
(illustrations 1024&times;1024), hand-painted watercolor, warm sunset-orange
palette, organic edges. Empty-state illustrations may be wider (4:3).
</div>

</body>
</html>
